  .container
    .section-title
      Everything in one place
    %p.centered
      At Nuwe, we understand that there is no one <nobr>single solution. </nobr>
      <nobr>So we make</nobr> it as easy as possible to use all of them, regardless  of the platform, device or services you want to support.

    .row.centered.stack
      .column.nw-service
        .nw-service-logo
          %img{:src => "<!-- @path nuwe-service-logo.png -->"}
        .nw-service-description
          Access to wearables such as Moves, Fit Bit and Withings direct from the Nuwe Platform.
        .nw-switch
          %input#service_1_enabled.toggle_application{:checked => "checked", :name => "service_3_enabled", :type => "checkbox", :value => "19"}
            %label{:for => "service_1_enabled"} Service 3 enabled
      .column.nw-service
        .nw-service-logo
          %img{:src => "<!-- @path valdic-service-logo.png -->"}
        .nw-service-description
          A world of digital health data. One easy connection.
        .nw-switch
          %input#service_2_enabled.toggle_application{:name => "service_3_enabled", :type => "checkbox", :value => "19"}
            %label{:for => "service_2_enabled"} Service 3 enabled
      .column.nw-service
        .nw-service-logo
          %img{:src => "<!-- @path humanapi-service-logo.png -->"}
        .nw-service-description
          Easily integrate health data from anywhere
